{"title":"2020-07-01","virtualPath":"/Diary/","html":"<p>とうとうきた。<g-emoji class=\"g-emoji\" alias=\"100\" fallback-src=\"https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f4af.png\">💯</g-emoji></p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-07-01/20200701-181457-Screenshot_20200701-181457.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-07-01/20200701-181457-Screenshot_20200701-181457.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>夢ではない。<g-emoji class=\"g-emoji\" alias=\"grinning\" fallback-src=\"https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f600.png\">😀</g-emoji> いつも通り 金ズリ Excellent カーブ連チャンで当ててるのにラスト二投でやっと入る。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-07-01/20200701-181732-Screenshot_20200701-181732.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-07-01/20200701-181732-Screenshot_20200701-181732.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>なんか今日に限ってどうでもいい子達もいっぱい <g-emoji class=\"g-emoji\" alias=\"100\" fallback-src=\"https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f4af.png\">💯</g-emoji> ひっかかってた。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-07-01/20200701-201046-Screenshot_20200701-201046.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-07-01/20200701-201046-Screenshot_20200701-201046.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"img/2020/2020-07-01/20200701-201050-Screenshot_20200701-201050.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-07-01/20200701-201050-Screenshot_20200701-201050.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"img/2020/2020-07-01/20200701-201053-Screenshot_20200701-201053.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-07-01/20200701-201053-Screenshot_20200701-201053.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>ゼクロム… 頑張った甲斐があった… <strong>感無量である。</strong> 解放もしてあげたいので、血反吐吐きながらアメ集めよう。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>二体目のキラゼクロム。やったねっ <g-emoji class=\"g-emoji\" alias=\"middle_finger\" fallback-src=\"https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f595.png\">🖕</g-emoji></p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-07-01/20200701-084553-Screenshot_20200701-084553.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-07-01/20200701-084553-Screenshot_20200701-084553.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"日記","updated":"2020-07-04T02:27:29","published":"2020-07-04T02:27:29"}